The game Smasandyutakankarikrida is played by two players on a noshape board with nobasis tiling. All players play with Markers. Rules for Pieces: Markers step adjacent or hop adjacent. Players take turns moving. Setup: Place a Marker for player one at the union of the bottom sites of the board expanded by 1 steps and I3 expanded by 5 steps. Place a Marker for player two at the union of the top sites of the board expanded by 1 steps and A7 expanded by 5 steps.. Rules: Move one of your pieces. Aim: If there are no pieces owned by Player the next player, the next player loses. The Smasandyutakankarikrida (Ludii 1) ruleset.
